===Etymology===
{{PIE root|en|bʰrewh₁}}
{{etyl|enm|en}} {{m|enm|brewen}}, from {{etyl|ang|en}} {{m|ang|brēowan}}, from {{etyl|gem-pro|en}} {{m|gem-pro|*brewwaną}}, from {{etyl|ine-pro|en}} {{m|ine-pro|*bʰrewh₁-}}, {{m|ine-pro|*bʰreh₁w-}} (compare Welsh {{m|cy|berw||boiling}}, Latin {{m|la|fervēre}}, Albanian {{m|sq|mbruaj||to knead}}, Russian {{m|ru|бруя́||current}}, Sanskrit {{m|sa|भुर्वन्||motion of water|tr=bhurván}}).

